  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You can enjoy an extensive continental buffet breakfast with a wide choice of hot and cold dishes, including freshly baked pastries and breads.</p>
<p>Half Board and Full Board options are available at a supplement. </p>
<p>*Please note that half board is compulsory on stays between 08 - 22 Aug 2020</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
