  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>R</strong><strong>estaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p>The restaurant at the Continental Mare is framed by large windows that overlook the sea and serves local dishes made using fresh, local produce. After dinner, you can head to the bar relax with a cocktail.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pools &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>There are two thermal pools at the hotel, heated to different temperatures. The garden pool is 30 °C and is surrounded by a spacious lawn with plenty of spots to sunbath. The second pool is 28 °C and is located on the panoramic terrace where you can enjoy spectacular views of the coast of Naples.</p>
<p>A private rocky beach is also available for guest’s use and is accessed by a number of steps.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>Club Benessere Mare Mare is located at the hotel and offers massages and beauty treatments. You can also take a free shuttle to the state-of-the-art wellness centre at the sister Hotel Continental Terme where expert staff will help you to choose the right tailored plan for you.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Wifi in all areas</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
