  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> sleep up to three adults or two adults and two children and measure between 18-26m². Facilities include a terrace or balcony with garden views, air conditioning, TV, minibar, safe and hairdryer. Baby cots are available on request (apporx. €20 per day)</p>
<p><strong>Single Occupancy Comfort Rooms </strong>are available for solo travelers. </p>
<p><strong>Sea View Rooms</strong> have stunning sea views from the balcony and can accommodate up to four adults.</p>
<p><strong>Single Occupancy Sea View Rooms </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
